            <row>
              <entry>makes:1.9 develops a plan for making that includes all of the following:<list id="id7889526" list-type="bulleted"><item>resources needed ;</item><item>sketches showing the necessary dimensions or quantities;</item><item>all the steps necessary to make the product;</item></list></entry>
