            <row>
              <entry>communicates:1.14 presents ideas (in a project portfolio) using two-dimensional or three-dimensional sketches, circuit diagrams or systems diagrams that include all of the following:<list id="id1168993812196" list-type="bulleted"><item>conventional drawing conventions (e.g. dimension lines, labelling, line types, symbols);</item><item>notes to clarify and communicate design fea­tures and reasoning; enhancement of significant sketches like final solution drawings (e.g. colour, shade, texture, shadow, thick and thin lines).</item></list></entry>
